  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Admin Assistant",
  "description": "<p>To provide general administrative duties, support the sales team and other ad hoc duties when required.<br /></p><p><strong>Handle frontline clerical duties:</strong></p><ul><li>Attend to telephone calls and answering general enquiries</li><li>Receive walk-in visitors</li><li>Provide general administrative and project-based work support</li></ul><p><strong>Support duties:</strong></p><ul><li>Key in invoices</li><li>Receiving stocks</li><li>Transferring stocks</li><li>Inventories control</li></ul><p>Working Hours:</p><ul><li>Monday to Friday - 8.30am to 5.45pm</li><li>alternate Saturdays - 8.30am to 12.30pm</li></ul><h3>Requirements</h3><ul><li>West area</li><li>Skill: Knowledge of Adobe Photoshop</li><li>Min. O’ Levels or equivalent with passes in English, Chinese and Mathematics</li><li>Bilingual in English and Chinese, both oral and written so as to communicate with Mandarin speaking customers / suppliers</li><li>At least 1 year of similar working experience is a plus.</li><li>Team player and a fast learner, someone who is energetic with good people management skills and able to work independently in a fast paced environment.</li><li>Able to start immediately.</li><li>Singaporeans only.</li></ul><p><br />\n\n</p>",
